  "text": "LV endocardial systolic function was assessed by biplane Simpson's ejection fraction (low if <50%) [CITATION_1] . Circumferential end-systolic stress was calculated at midwall using a cylindrical model, and peak systolic stress was estimated from systolic blood pressure and end-diastolic LV dimensions taking into account the mean aortic valve gradient and using an invasively validated equation [CITATION_2] .",
